width="1600"
height="900"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/07-population_hu6423403011203823444.jpg 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/07-population_hu13559723732849914508.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="population"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>然而，每页最多显示 50 条数据，
寻找目标职位需要通过职位代码定位，
也就是说需要多次翻页：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/08-query.jpg"
width="1600"
height="900"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/08-query_hu346505014853977676.jpg 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/08-query_hu9232658865722913741.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="query"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>而且，如果翻页过于频繁还会弹窗拒绝：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/09-rate-limit.jpg"
width="1600"
height="900"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/09-rate-limit_hu17853823389679884324.jpg 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240323-civil-exam-sign/img/09-rate-limit_hu2072452384967036717.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="rate limit"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>也就是说，如果筛选了60个职位，
每次查询至少需要1分钟，
则完成一轮查询需要1小时！&lt;/p>
